### =====================================================================
### Ticket API  (base route: api/ticket/)  TagTicket: 101 SuperAdmin, 102 Admin
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Create - full
POST {{host}}/api/ticket/Create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "title": "Payment failed",
  "description": "I could not complete my payment.",
  "tags": [102],
  "phone": "+989120000000",
  "telegram": "@support"
}

### Create - minimal (title + description + tags)
POST {{host}}/api/ticket/Create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "title": "Feature request",
  "description": "Please add dark mode.",
  "tags": [101]
}

### Read
POST {{host}}/api/ticket/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "tags": [102],
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Update
POST {{host}}/api/ticket/Update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "description": "Updated details"
}

### Delete
POST {{host}}/api/ticket/Delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}
